properties.html:
Look Deep Into The Nature

How Hypo's Water Treatment Solutions Protect Public Health and the Environment

learn more

Water Treatment for Household

Makes Water Safe for Reuse

Environment Substainability

Water Scarcity

HYPO, our cutting-edge water treatment product that is poised to revolutionize groundwater management practices. In an era where sustainable solutions are paramount, HYPO stands out by effectively treating and recycling groundwater, ensuring the elimination of harmful contaminants and making previously unusable water safe for reuse. This remarkable innovation not only enhances the quality of water but significantly alleviates the strain on our finite freshwater resources, promoting a more sustainable future for us all.

Water Contamination

Hypo is specially formulated to eliminate toxic waste and impurities from water sources, making the water safe for reuse. This not only protects public health but also helps preserve aquatic ecosystems.

By using Hypo, industries can effectively treat wastewater before it is released back into the environment, ensuring a safe and sustainable approach to water management. 

Bridging Demand- Supply Gap

About Us
Welcome to Aquaeva Chemtech Pvt Ltd

We are a leading manufacturer of calcium Hypochlorite with a core focus in providingclean water for
Household and industries

Aquaeva Chemtech Pvt Ltd., a prominent leader in the chemical industry, committed toinnovation and sustainability. Founded with a vision to make a significant impact on environmental caretaking, our company has carved a niche in themanufacturing of high-quality calcium hypochlorite. This essential chemical serves as a key component in the processes of water treatment and recycling,allowing municipalities and businesses alike to ensure clean and safe water for their communities.
At Aquaeva Chemtech, we pride ourselves on our unwavering dedication toaddressing pressing environmental challenges while promoting economic growth. This commitment is not mere rhetoric; it is central to our operations andreflects in the quality of our products and the integrity of our processes. We firmly believe that through collaborative efforts, we can achieve significantadvancements in sustainable practices, thereby fostering employment opportunities and contributing to our shared goals of environmental stewardshipand community development.

A

Aquaeva Chemtech's unwavering commitment to tackling one of the most pressing challenges of our time: clean water scarcity in both the household and industrial sectors. Our mission goes beyond just providing water solutions; we are dedicated to fostering a world where access to safe and clean water is a right, not a privilege.

Vision and Mission

We emphasize the core principles that underpin our work culture. We pride ourselves on our commitment to fair trade practices and ethical values. These principles guide our operations and ensure that we deliver high-quality chemicals to our clients promptly. Our comprehensive supply chain network is designed to support these commitments, 

Values

Our Founder and Management Team

Founder and MD

Director

Director

"Hypo"

  • Introducing Hypo - the revolutionary water purification system that's redefining the way we think about clean water. Engineered with the latest advancements in water treatment technology, Hypo removes an astounding 99.9% of contaminants, heavy metals, and other impurities, giving you the purest, safest water possible.
  • Removes 99.9% of toxins, heavy metals, and other harmful substances
  • Recycles water to reduce waste and minimize environmental impact
  • Backed by rigoro​us lab testing for consistent, reliable performance
  • Compact, user-friendly design for easy installation anywhere
  • Hypo is the solution for those who demand the highest standards of water purity and sustainability. Experience the difference clean, sustainable water can make in your life and join the movement towards a healthier, more responsible future.

Problems the Hypo is solving

  • 1. Water Scarcity : One of the primary problems we are addressing is water scarcity. With increasing demand for clean water in both household and industrial sectors, the availability of safe, reusable water is becoming limited. By treating and recycling groundwater, Hypo helps to alleviate the pressure on fresh water resources, ensuring a more sustainable water supply for the future. 
  • 2. Water Contamination : Industrial processes often result in the release of toxic waste and impurities into water sources, posing significant health and environmental risks. Hypo is specifically formulated to eliminate these contaminants, making the water safe for reuse. This not only protects public health but also helps in preserving aquatic ecosystems. 
  • 3. Environmental Sustainability: Aquaeva Chemtech Pvt Ltd. is committed to providing eco-friendly solutions that reduce the environmental impact of water use. Our product helps in minimizing the waste generated by industrial activities, promoting sustainable practices that contribute to the conservation of natural resources. By offering a reliable and effective water treatment solution, we are playing a crucial role in advancing environmental sustainability. 
  • 4. Bridging the Demand-Supply Gap:  There is a significant gap between the demand for water treatment solutions and the available supply. Many industries and households are seeking sustainable methods to treat and reuse water, but the market does not yet fully cater to this demand. Aquaeva Chemtech Pvt Ltd. aims to bridge this gap by providing high-quality, affordable products that meet the needs of a growing market. 
  • 5. Enhancing Industrial Efficiency: Efficient water management is essential for industrial operations. Hypo not only purifies water but also ensures that industries have a consistent supply of clean water, which is critical for maintaining their processes. This enhances operational efficiency, reduces costs associated with water procurement, and supports regulatory compliance.
